languages.text: {n}Потрясенный ропот пробегает по рядам солдат. Чье-то лицо кривится в рыданиях, кто-то сжимает кулаки и шепчет проклятья.{/n}
{n}A shocked murmur runs through the ranks. One fighter sobs, his face twisted in grief, while another whispers a string of curses, his fists clenched.{/n}

languages.text: {n}隊列に衝撃のざわめきが走る。ある戦士は悲しみに顔をゆがめながら嗚咽し、別のひとりは、握りしめた拳で呪いの言葉を囁いている。{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}A shocked murmur runs through the ranks. One fighter sobs, his face twisted in grief, while another whispers a string of curses, his fists clenched.{/n}

languages.text: {n}震惊的低语声传遍了人群。一名战士满面痛苦，啜泣起来，另一个战士握紧了拳头，低声咒骂着。{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}A shocked murmur runs through the ranks. One fighter sobs, his face twisted in grief, while another whispers a string of curses, his fists clenched.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}震惊的低语声传遍了人群，一名战士的表情因悲痛而扭曲着，另一个人握紧了拳头，低声咒骂着。{/n}
traits.speaker: ImperialSoldier_Ranged_Prison

languages.text: {n}Un murmullo de sorpresa recorre las filas. Un luchador solloza con una mueca de dolor, mientras que otro susurra una retahíla de maldiciones con los puños cerrados.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}A shocked murmur runs through the ranks. One fighter sobs, his face twisted in grief, while another whispers a string of curses, his fists clenched.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}Un murmullo de sorpresa recorre las filas. La expresión de un luchador se retuerce de lamento. Otro susurra una retahíla de maldiciones con los puños cerrados.{/n}
traits.speaker: ImperialSoldier_Ranged_Prison

languages.text: {n}Ein entsetztes Raunen geht durch die Reihen. Während ein Kämpfer zu weinen beginnt, stößt ein anderer mit geballten Fäusten ein Tirade von Flüchen aus.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}A shocked murmur runs through the ranks. One fighter sobs, his face twisted in grief, while another whispers a string of curses, his fists clenched.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}Ein entsetztes Raunen geht durch die Reihen. Einem Kämpfer steht völlig Niedergeschlagenheit ins Gesicht geschrieben. Ein anderer flüstert mit geballten Fäusten zornige Verwünschungen.{/n}
traits.speaker: ImperialSoldier_Ranged_Prison

languages.text: {n}Une vague de murmures choqués parcourt l'assemblée. L'un des combattants sanglote, le visage tordu par la tristesse, tandis qu'un autre profère des jurons en serrant les poings.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}A shocked murmur runs through the ranks. One fighter sobs, his face twisted in grief, while another whispers a string of curses, his fists clenched.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}Une vague de murmures choqués parcourt les rangs. Certains se mettent à se lamenter, tandis que d'autres profèrent des jurons en serrant les poings.{/n}
traits.speaker: ImperialSoldier_Ranged_Prison

languages.text: {n}Savaşçılar, hayret içinde mırıldanıyor. İçlerinden birinin yüzü kederle şekilden şekle girmiş, hıçkırarak ağlarken bir ötekiyse yumruklarını sıka sıka, mırıldanarak lanet okuyor.{/n}
